View Member's: Reviews These people have two clauses in their terms and conditions which are against the terms of the Sale of Goods Act. Manic Deals will not pay return postage for faulty goods they supply and they only deem goods to be faulty if they decide they are so. Manic Deals is unhelpful and unfriendly if things go wrong and, basically, the buyer loses out. Avoid. Overall Rating
